    .hero-unit
      %p
        Whenever my brothers and I get together, a discussion along the lines of
        'who is the greatest rock band of all time' or 'who would win in a
        fight, John McEnroe with a tennis racket or Mike Tyson in boxing gloves'?

      %p
        Since my brother was stuck on his deployment to Germany over winter
        break 2012, we didn't get to settle one of these. So I built this app to
        let us continue iterating towards ultimate truth even while he's
        overseas.

      %p

